[[加雷斯·贝尔|加雷斯·贝尔]]是威尔士职业[[足球|足球]]运动员，2006年开始担任[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯足球代表隊]][[前鋒_(足球)|前锋]]。2006年5月，他在[[熱身賽|友谊赛]]首次代表威尔士出战，对抗[[千里達及托巴哥國家足球隊|特立尼达和多巴哥队]]，是有纪录以来该队最年轻的国际赛事上场球员<ref>{{Cite web | access-date = 2020-07-14 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190827182955/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/5024788.stm | publisher = [[BBC體育|BBC Sport]] | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/5024788.stm | title = Bale savours record Wales debut | date = 2006-05-28 | archivedate = 2019-08-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。同年10月，他在[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛外围赛|2008年欧洲足球锦标赛资格赛]]第三次代表威尔士出场，并以任意球直接破门，帮助球队以5比1大胜[[斯洛伐克國家足球隊|斯洛伐克队]]，又成为威尔士历史上最年轻的得分射手<ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/5361822.stm | title = Wales 1–5 Slovakia | last = Davies | first = Sean | date = 2006-10-07 | access-date = 2020-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190806061900/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/5361822.stm | archivedate = 2019-08-06 }}</ref>。截至2021年9月，贝尔共上场99次，进球36颗，两项都创下威尔士的新纪录<ref>{{cite web | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20211019053314/https://www.11v11.com/teams/wales/tab/stats/option/scorers/ | deadurl = no | url = https://www.11v11.com/teams/wales/tab/stats/option/scorers/ | title = Wales national football team statistics and records: top scorers | website = 11v11.com | publisher = AFS Enterprises | accessdate = 2021-10-29 | archivedate = 2021-10-19 }}</ref>。

2015年10月13日，贝尔在[[2016年歐洲足球錦標賽|2016年歐洲足球錦標賽]]最后一场资格赛中破门，是他在国际比赛中第19次进球，帮助威尔士队以2比0战胜[[安道爾國家足球隊|安道尔队]]，并在[[1958年國際足協世界盃|1958年國際足協世界盃]]后首度杀入国际大型赛事<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/33544105 | title = Wales 2–0 Andorra | publisher = BBC Sport | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190730222833/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/33544105 | last = Pritchard | first = Dafydd | deadurl = no | date = 2015-10-13 | access-date = 2020-07-14 | archivedate = 2019-07-30 }}</ref>。凭借该轮资格赛七次进球，贝尔成为球队最佳射手<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.fourfourtwo.com/features/infographic-top-scorers-euro-2016-qualifying | title = Infographic: The top scorers in Euro 2016 qualifying | work = [[442_(雜誌)|FourFourTwo]] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190815061959/https://www.fourfourtwo.com/features/infographic-top-scorers-euro-2016-qualifying | last = Mayhew | first = Ben | date = 2016-06-08 | access-date = 2020-07-14 | archivedate = 2019-08-15 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。接下来他在三局分组赛均有得分，帮助威尔士队击败斯洛伐克队和[[俄羅斯國家足球隊|俄罗斯队]]杀入半决赛<ref name="rsssf">{{cite web | url = http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/bale-intlg.html | title = Gareth Bale – Goals in International Matches | publisher = [[RSSSF|The Rec.Sport.Soccer Statistics Foundation]] | last = Mamrud | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191227033944/http://www.rsssf.com/miscellaneous/bale-intlg.html | first = Roberto | access-date = 2020-07-04 | archivedate = 2019-12-27 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。贝尔在分组赛首场对阵斯洛伐克队时率先进球，是1958年[[特里·梅德温|特里·梅德温]]（{{lang|en|Terry Medwin}}）打入[[匈牙利國家足球隊|匈牙利队]]大门后威尔士球员首度在国际重大赛事破门<ref>{{cite news | access-date = 2020-07-14 | archivedate = 2019-08-06 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20190806091233/https://www.southwalesargus.co.uk/sport/14551725.euro-2016-wales-2-slovakia-1/ | url = https://www.southwalesargus.co.uk/sport/14551725.euro-2016-wales-2-slovakia-1/ | title = Euro 2016: Wales 2 Slovakia 1 | newspaper = South Wales Argus | last = Penman | first = Andrew | date = 2016-06-11 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。2018年3月22日，他在[[2018年中国杯国际足球锦标赛|中国杯]]对战[[中国国家足球队|中国队]]的友谊赛中达成[[帽子戲法|帽子戲法]]，刷新威尔士队球员的国际赛事进球总数纪录<ref name="sw">{{Cite web | access-date = 2020-07-14 | url = https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2018/03/22/world/china-cup/china-pr/wales/2698851/?ICID=PL_MS_01 | title = China PR v Wales | date = 2018-03-22 | website = Soccerway | archive-date = 2021-10-17 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211017131106/https://int.soccerway.com/matches/2018/03/22/world/china-cup/china-pr/wales/2698851/?ICID=PL_MS_01 }}</ref>。比赛开始前，贝尔已进球26次，比同胞[[伊恩·拉什|伊恩·拉什]]2016年11月创下的纪录差两分<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/43501828 | title = Gareth Bale says becoming Wales' record scorer is career highlight | publisher = BBC Sport | date = 2018-03-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191115081327/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/43501828 | access-date = 2020-07-14 | archivedate = 2019-11-15 | deadurl = no }}</ref>，他在上半场就获得两分，追平拉什的纪录，下半场又拿下第三分，打破纪录以余，还成为2004年[[羅拔·安梳爾|羅拔·安梳爾]]后威尔士队首位在国际比赛达成帽子戏法的球员<ref>{{cite news | url = https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/43465791 | title = China PR 0–6 Wales | publisher = BBC Sport | last = Pritchard | first = Dafydd | date = 2018-03-22 | access-date = 2020-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20191115080743/https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/43465791 | archivedate = 2019-11-15 }}</ref>。2021年9月他再度达成帽子戏法，为球队三比二战胜[[白俄羅斯國家足球隊|白俄罗斯]]立下汗马功劳<ref name="BLR" />。

从[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛|2008年欧洲足球锦标赛]]开始，贝尔在每次[[國際足協世界盃|國際足協世界盃]]和[[欧洲足球锦标赛|欧洲足球锦标赛]]期间都随威尔士队出征，还曾护送球队打入2016年歐洲足球錦標賽半决赛，但不敌最终冠军[[葡萄牙國家足球隊|葡萄牙队]]<ref>{{Cite web | url = https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/36658962 | title = Portugal 2–0 Wales | last = McNulty | first = Phil | date = 2016-07-06 | publisher = BBC Sport | access-date = 2020-07-14 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20200705092335/https://www.bbc.com/sport/football/36658962 | archivedate = 2020-07-05 }}</ref>。他在资格赛中共打入27球，超过其他任一球员。他在友谊赛共进球六次（上述的中国杯比赛三次），2016年欧洲足球錦標賽决赛圈比赛三次，[[歐洲足協國家聯賽|歐洲足協國家聯賽]]两次。<ref name="rsssf" />贝尔进球最多的对手是[[中华人民共和国|中国]]、[[白俄罗斯|白俄罗斯]]、[[安道尔|安道尔]]和[[奥地利|奥地利]]四支队伍，他对阵上述每队的总进球数均多达三个。<ref name="rsssf" />

